            "content": [
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": "अंग्रेजी भाषा में <b>8 प्रकार के Parts of Speech</b> हैं। हर शब्द इनमें से किसी एक category में आता है। इसे <b>Word Family</b> भी कहते हैं।"
                },
                {
                    "type": "table",
                    "content": {
                        "title": "🔄 8 Parts of Speech Overview",
                        "headers": ["#", "Part of Speech", "हिंदी में", "Quick Definition"],
                        "rows": [
                            ["1", "<b>Noun</b>", "संज्ञा", "Naming word (नाम) - Person, Place, Thing"],
                            ["2", "<b>Pronoun</b>", "सर्वनाम", "Replaces Noun - He, She, It, They"],
                            ["3", "<b>Verb</b>", "क्रिया", "Action/State word - Run, Is, Have"],
                            ["4", "<b>Adjective</b>", "विशेषण", "Describes Noun - Good, Big, Red"],
                            ["5", "<b>Adverb</b>", "क्रिया विशेषण", "Describes Verb - Slowly, Very, Now"],
                            ["6", "<b>Preposition</b>", "संबंधबोधक", "Shows relation - In, On, At, To"],
                            ["7", "<b>Conjunction</b>", "समुच्चयबोधक", "Joins words - And, But, Or, Because"],
                            ["8", "<b>Interjection</b>", "विस्मयादिबोधक", "Expresses emotion - Wow!, Oh!, Alas!"]
                        ]
                    }
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "section",
            "title": "1️⃣ Noun (संज्ञा)",
            "content": [
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": "किसी भी <b>व्यक्ति (Person), वस्तु (Thing), स्थान (Place), जानवर (Animal)</b> या <b>भाव (Idea/Feeling)</b> को दर्शाने वाले नाम को <b>Noun</b> कहते हैं।"
                },
                {
                    "type": "table",
                    "content": {
                        "title": "📋 Types of Noun",
                        "headers": ["Type", "हिंदी में", "Definition", "Examples"],
                        "rows": [
                            ["<b>Common Noun</b>", "जातिवाचक", "General name (सामान्य नाम)", "boy, city, book, river"],
                            ["<b>Proper Noun</b>", "व्यक्तिवाचक", "Specific name (विशेष नाम) - Capital letter", "Rahul, India, Ganga, Monday"],
                            ["<b>Collective Noun</b>", "समूहवाचक", "Group name (समूह का नाम)", "team, crowd, army, flock"],
                            ["<b>Material Noun</b>", "द्रव्यवाचक", "Substance name (पदार्थ का नाम)", "gold, water, wood, iron"],
                            ["<b>Abstract Noun</b>", "भाववाचक", "Quality/Feeling name (गुण/भाव का नाम)", "happiness, love, honesty, fear"]
                        ]
                    }
                },
                {
                    "type": "table",
                    "content": {
                        "title": "🔍 How to Identify Noun?",
                        "headers": ["Question", "Answer = Noun"],
                        "rows": [
                            ["<b>कौन?</b> (Who?)", "Rahul is playing. → <b>Rahul</b>"],
                            ["<b>क्या?</b> (What?)", "I bought a <b>book</b>."],
                            ["<b>कहाँ?</b> (Where?)", "He lives in <b>Mumbai</b>."]
                        ]
                    }
                },
                {
                    "type": "note",
                    "content": "<b>Pro Tip:</b> Proper Noun का पहला अक्षर हमेशा <b>Capital</b> होता है।<br>Example: <b>R</b>am, <b>I</b>ndia, <b>M</b>onday"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "section",
