                    }
                },
                {
                    "type": "note",
                    "content": "<b>Pro Tip:</b> Coordinating Conjunctions याद करने के लिए <b>FANBOYS</b> याद करें!<br><b>F</b>or, <b>A</b>nd, <b>N</b>or, <b>B</b>ut, <b>O</b>r, <b>Y</b>et, <b>S</b>o"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "section",
            "title": "8️⃣ Interjection (विस्मयादिबोधक)",
            "content": [
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": "मन में <b>अचानक उत्पन्न तीव्र भावनाओं</b> (joy, sorrow, surprise, fear) को व्यक्त करने वाले शब्दों को <b>Interjection</b> कहते हैं।"
                },
                {
                    "type": "table",
                    "content": {
                        "title": "📋 Types of Interjection",
                        "headers": ["Emotion", "Interjections", "Example Sentence"],
                        "rows": [
                            ["<b>Joy (खुशी)</b>", "Hurrah!, Wow!, Yay!", "<b>Hurrah!</b> We won the match!"],
                            ["<b>Sorrow (दुख)</b>", "Alas!, Oh no!", "<b>Alas!</b> He is no more."],
                            ["<b>Surprise (आश्चर्य)</b>", "Oh!, What!, Wow!", "<b>Oh!</b> What a beautiful place!"],
                            ["<b>Pain (पीड़ा)</b>", "Ouch!, Ow!", "<b>Ouch!</b> That hurts!"],
                            ["<b>Appreciation (प्रशंसा)</b>", "Bravo!, Well done!", "<b>Bravo!</b> You did it!"],
                            ["<b>Attention (ध्यान)</b>", "Hello!, Hey!, Look!", "<b>Hey!</b> Listen to me."]
                        ]
                    }
                },
                {
                    "type": "note",
                    "content": "<b>Pro Tip:</b> Interjection के बाद हमेशा <b>Exclamation Mark (!)</b> आता है!<br>Interjection वाक्य के व्याकरण का हिस्सा नहीं होता।"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "section",
            "title": "⚠️ Confusion Points (भ्रामक मुद्दे)",
