                            ["<b>क्रिया कैसे होती है?</b> (How the action?)", "→ Adverb"],
                            ["<b>कहाँ? कब? किस दिशा में?</b> (Where? When?)", "→ Preposition"],
                            ["<b>क्या जोड़ता है?</b> (What connects?)", "→ Conjunction"],
                            ["<b>अचानक भाव?</b> (Sudden emotion?)", "→ Interjection"]
                        ]
                    }
                },
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": "<b>Example:</b> \"<i>Wow! The beautiful girl runs quickly in the park.</i>\"<br><br>• <b>Wow!</b> - Interjection (अचानक भाव)<br>• <b>The</b> - Article (Adjective)<br>• <b>beautiful</b> - Adjective (कैसी girl?)<br>• <b>girl</b> - Noun (कौन?)<br>• <b>runs</b> - Verb (क्या करती है?)<br>• <b>quickly</b> - Adverb (कैसे runs?)<br>• <b>in</b> - Preposition (कहाँ?)<br>• <b>the</b> - Article<br>• <b>park</b> - Noun (क्या?)"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "section",
